## Retrieve a storage

> REQUEST

```bash
curl -X GET \
  <%= config[:endpoint] %>/media/storage?id=cd003123-7ec9-4f3a-9d7c-f2de93e83e49 \
  -H 'Authorization: <%= config[:token] %>'
```

```ruby
require "json"

Uiza.workspace_api_domain = "<%= config[:endpoint] %>"
Uiza.authorization = "<%= config[:token] %>"

